---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  lang="en"
  title="YWAM Sendai | Christian Community in Sendai, Japan"
  description="YWAM Sendai is a Christian missional community in Sendai, serving the wider Tohoku region through prayer, hospitality, discipleship, training, and faithful presence."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-inner">
      <div class="stack">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Christian Community in Sendai, Japan</p>
          <h1 class="hero-title max-w-title">
            A warm, rooted community for discipleship, mission, and long-term
            service in Tohoku.
          </h1>
        </div>

        <p class="lead">
          YWAM Sendai is a Christian community in Sendai, serving the wider
          Tohoku region through prayer, hospitality, training, and faithful presence.
        </p>

        <div class="btn-group">
          <button type="button" class="btn-primary open-hub-trigger">Ask AI</button>
          <a href="/en/dts" class="btn-secondary-dark">Explore DTS</a>
          <a href="/en/dbs" class="btn-secondary-dark">Explore DBS</a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-inverse-soft mb-0">
          Ask questions, explore programs, or find your next step.
        </p>

        <div class="btn-group">
          <a href="/en/apply" class="btn-text">Apply</a>
          <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-text">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card hero-feature-card stack-sm">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our Heart</p>
        <h2 class="card-title">Faithful presence in Sendai and Tohoku</h2>
        <p>
          We want to know God and make Him known through prayer, shared life,
          discipleship, hospitality, and long-term service in this region.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Who We Are</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">
          More than a program. A community rooted in prayer and mission.
        </h2>
        <p class="lead">
          We seek to know God and make Him known through shared life, discipleship, and service.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Prayer and worship</h3>
          <p>Mission begins with devotion to Jesus.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Discipleship and formation</h3>
          <p>We care about character, calling, and faithfulness.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3 class="card-title">Hospitality and shared life</h3>
          <p>Community is something we live together.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2" style="align-items: start;">
        <div class="stack-sm">
          <p class="eyebrow">Rooted in Place</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Rooted in Sendai. Serving Tohoku.</h2>
          <p class="lead">
            We believe mission is most faithful when it is rooted in real people and real places.
          </p>
          <p class="text-soft">
            From Sendai, we seek to serve the wider Tohoku region through long-term presence,
            local relationships, and partnership with the church.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid stack-sm">
          <article class="card card-interactive">
            <h3 class="card-title">Long-term presence</h3>
            <p>Choosing faithfulness over speed.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card card-interactive">
            <h3 class="card-title">Cultural humility</h3>
            <p>Learning language, listening well, and serving with respect.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card card-interactive">
            <h3 class="card-title">Regional partnership</h3>
            <p>Walking with churches and communities across Tohoku.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Next Steps</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Explore your next step</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Whether you are just beginning to explore or ready to move forward, here are a few ways to connect.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-4">
        <article class="card card-interactive">
          <span class="chip-accent">School</span>
          <h3 class="card-title">DTS</h3>
          <p>A season of discipleship, spiritual formation, and mission training.</p>
          <a href="/en/dts" class="btn-text">Explore DTS</a>
        </article>

        <article class="card card-interactive">
          <span class="chip-accent">School</span>
          <h3 class="card-title">DBS</h3>
          <p>A deeper journey into Scripture, formation, and life with God’s Word.</p>
          <a href="/en/dbs" class="btn-text">Explore DBS</a>
        </article>

        <article class="card surface-accent card-interactive">
          <span class="chip-accent">Guide</span>
          <h3 class="card-title">Not sure where to begin?</h3>
          <p>Ask the AI assistant about programs, applying, the handbook, or your next step.</p>
          <button type="button" class="btn-text open-hub-trigger">Ask AI</button>
        </article>

        <article class="card card-interactive">
          <span class="chip-accent">Partner</span>
          <h3 class="card-title">Support the Mission</h3>
          <p>Partner with long-term ministry and community life in Tohoku.</p>
          <a href="/en/give" class="btn-text">Donate</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-intro container-narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our Life Together</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Formed for faithful presence</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          We care not only about what we do, but about who we are becoming.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-4">
        <article class="card-dark">
          <h3 class="card-title">Prayer and worship</h3>
          <p>A life centered on Jesus.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card-dark">
          <h3 class="card-title">Scripture and discipleship</h3>
          <p>Formation for both inner life and outward service.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card-dark">
          <h3 class="card-title">Hospitality and community</h3>
          <p>Shared life, generosity, and welcome.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="card-dark">
          <h3 class="card-title">Long-term service</h3>
          <p>Sustainable rhythms of work, rest, and mission.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-paper border-top">
    <div class="container container-narrow center stack">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Start Here</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Start where you are</h2>
        <p class="lead mx-auto">
          Whether you are exploring YWAM Sendai, considering a school, or looking for the right page,
          we would love to help you take the next step.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
        <button type="button" class="btn-primary open-hub-trigger">Ask AI</button>
        <a href="/en/apply" class="btn-secondary">Apply</a>
      </div>

      <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-text">Contact</a>
        <a href="/en/give" class="btn-text">Donate</a>
        <a href="https://guide.ywamsendai.org/en" class="btn-text" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Visit Handbook</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>